  "title": "Feat/new range slider",
  "body": "⚠️ merge first https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/pull/2107 I will re-open the PR after on the correct branch, this is just for keeping track of what is done and code review.\r\n\r\nUse https://github.com/airbnb/rheostat as `range-slider` and should remove the usage of https://github.com/algolia/react-nouislider which is not meant to be maintained.\r\n\r\n* fixes range slider issues with negatives values 🎉\r\n* removes the \"hacky\" JS -> React bridge for nouislider\r\n* tries to keep the same options as before for easy replacement for current client implementations\r\n* fixes the wrong calculation of the \"half\" value (never got reported?)\r\n\r\n### TODO:\r\n\r\n* [x] POC\r\n* [x] Tests\r\n* [x] Remove legacy range-slider\r\n* [x] Improve styles\r\n\r\n### PREVIEW:\r\n\r\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/893837/25142166/52aa2e84-2466-11e7-8946-1a7e3a85dfb2.png)\r\n\r\n(price2)\r\n",
